    <comment>hobbits 0.55.0. Add detail darix asked for: the bundled pffft FFT lib is bumped to the 2025-02-24 snapshot d7a4c02 (vendored via Source1 as upstream pulls it in as a git submodule not in the release tarball). Build with -fsigned-char (bitarray.cpp char[] bit masks use negative literals, a narrowing error where char is unsigned, e.g. aarch64). Build with Ninja via %cmake_build.</comment>
